  <script>
  /**
   * Appstle Bundle Sync Fix for "Digital" Theme
   * Monitors network activity for cart changes and forces theme to update.
   */
  (function(ns, fetch) {
    if (typeof fetch !== 'function') return;

    ns.fetch = function() {
      const response = fetch.apply(this, arguments);

      response.then(res => {
        if (res.url.includes('/cart/add') || res.url.includes('/cart/update') || res.url.includes('/cart/change')) {
          
          // 1. Wait briefly for Appstle to finish its data work
          setTimeout(() => {
            
            // --- Method A: Standard OS 2.0 Events ---
            document.documentElement.dispatchEvent(new CustomEvent('cart:refresh', { bubbles: true }));
            document.documentElement.dispatchEvent(new CustomEvent('cart:update', { bubbles: true }));

            // --- Method B: Legacy/Third-Party Theme Events (Likely for "Digital") ---
            if (window.theme && window.theme.ajaxCart && typeof window.theme.ajaxCart.update === 'function') {
               window.theme.ajaxCart.update();
            }
            if (typeof refreshCart === 'function') {
               refreshCart();
            }
            
            // --- Method C: jQuery Triggers (Old reliable) ---
            if (window.jQuery) {
              window.jQuery('body').trigger('added.ajaxProduct');
              window.jQuery('body').trigger('updateCart');
            }

            // --- Method D: UI Force Update (The fallback) ---
            // If the drawer exists but didn't open/update, we fetch the fresh HTML manually
            const cartDrawer = document.querySelector('#cart-drawer, .cart-drawer, .mini-cart');
            if (cartDrawer) {
              fetch(window.Shopify.routes.root + "?sections=cart-drawer,cart-notification-product,cart-notification-button")
                .then(r => r.json())
                .then(data => {
                    // Update specific sections if they exist in the response
                    const drawerData = data['cart-drawer'] || data['cart-notification-product'];
                    if (drawerData) {
                        // Find the inner container to replace (adjust selector if needed)
                        const inner = cartDrawer.querySelector('.cart-drawer__items, .mini-cart-content') || cartDrawer;
                        inner.innerHTML = drawerData;
                    }
                });
            }

          }, 500); // 500ms delay to ensure Appstle is done
        }
      });

      return response;
    };
  }(window, window.fetch));
</script>

 document.addEventListener("DOMContentLoaded", () => {

  const redirect = params.get("redirect");

  // Prefill email
  if (email) {
    const emailInput = document.querySelector('input[name="customer[email]"]');
    emailInput && (emailInput.value = email);
  }

  // Shopify return_to redirect fix

  if (redirect && returnInput) {
    returnInput.value = redirect.startsWith("/") ? redirect : "/" + redirect;
  }
});

<script>
  
  const passwordField = document.querySelectorAll(".field--pass");

	passwordField.forEach((el) => {
		const input = el.querySelector("input");
		const btnWrapper = el.querySelector(".button-pass-visibility");
		const btnOpen = el.querySelector(".icon-eye-close");
		const btnClose = el.querySelector(".icon-eye");

		input.addEventListener("input", () => {
		input.value !== "" ? (btnWrapper.style.display = "block") : (btnWrapper.style.display = "none");
		});

		btnOpen.addEventListener("click", () => {
		input.type = "text";
		btnOpen.style.display = "none";
		btnClose.style.display = "block";
		});

		btnClose.addEventListener("click", () => {
		input.type = "password";
		btnOpen.style.display = "block";
		btnClose.style.display = "none";
		});
	});
</script>

  <script>
  /**
   * Appstle Bundle Sync Fix for "Digital" Theme
   * Monitors network activity for cart changes and forces theme to update.
   */
  (function(ns, fetch) {
    if (typeof fetch !== 'function') return;

    ns.fetch = function() {
      const response = fetch.apply(this, arguments);

      response.then(res => {
        if (res.url.includes('/cart/add') || res.url.includes('/cart/update') || res.url.includes('/cart/change')) {
          
          // 1. Wait briefly for Appstle to finish its data work
          setTimeout(() => {
            
            // --- Method A: Standard OS 2.0 Events ---
            document.documentElement.dispatchEvent(new CustomEvent('cart:refresh', { bubbles: true }));
            document.documentElement.dispatchEvent(new CustomEvent('cart:update', { bubbles: true }));

            // --- Method B: Legacy/Third-Party Theme Events (Likely for "Digital") ---
            if (window.theme && window.theme.ajaxCart && typeof window.theme.ajaxCart.update === 'function') {
               window.theme.ajaxCart.update();
            }
            if (typeof refreshCart === 'function') {
               refreshCart();
            }
            
            // --- Method C: jQuery Triggers (Old reliable) ---
            if (window.jQuery) {
              window.jQuery('body').trigger('added.ajaxProduct');
              window.jQuery('body').trigger('updateCart');
            }

            // --- Method D: UI Force Update (The fallback) ---
            // If the drawer exists but didn't open/update, we fetch the fresh HTML manually
            const cartDrawer = document.querySelector('#cart-drawer, .cart-drawer, .mini-cart');
            if (cartDrawer) {
              fetch(window.Shopify.routes.root + "?sections=cart-drawer,cart-notification-product,cart-notification-button")
                .then(r => r.json())
                .then(data => {
                    // Update specific sections if they exist in the response
                    const drawerData = data['cart-drawer'] || data['cart-notification-product'];
                    if (drawerData) {
                        // Find the inner container to replace (adjust selector if needed)
                        const inner = cartDrawer.querySelector('.cart-drawer__items, .mini-cart-content') || cartDrawer;
                        inner.innerHTML = drawerData;
                    }
                });
            }

          }, 500); // 500ms delay to ensure Appstle is done
        }
      });

      return response;
    };
  }(window, window.fetch));
</script>
